<section>
  <p class="eyebrow">Application</p>
  <h2>How this becomes public practice</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <article class="card"><span class="status status-implemented">small group</span><h3>Conversation reset</h3><p>Before deciding content, name the mode: question, accusation, command, warning, plea, joke, or negotiation.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><span class="status status-implemented">institution</span><h3>Public process</h3><p>Require officials to speak in a mode they would accept in return: clear terms, traceable reasons, proportionate consequences.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><span class="status status-implemented">self-governance</span><h3>Personal practice</h3><p>Ask whether your speech invites understanding, defense, obedience, contempt, or repair.</p></article>
